id\u2019ah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahmah ibn Yazid reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cModeration in the Sunnah is better than striving in innovation.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak 289 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0650\u0627\u0642\u0652\u062a\u0650\u0635\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37417,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/23\/taqseer-salah-journey\/","url_meta":{"origin":33238,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Sunnah to shorten prayer during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Muwarriq al-\u2018Ijli reported: He asked Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about prayer during travel. Ibn Umar said, \u201cTwo cycles, two cycles. Whoever opposes the Sunnah has disbelieved.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf 'Abd al-Razza\u0304q 4281 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0651\u0642\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u062c\u0652\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u0636\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24122,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/05\/bidah-replaces-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33238,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bid&#8217;ah: Every religious innovation erases a Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ghudayf ibn al-Harith reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPeople do not contrive an innovation in religion but that it removes a Sunnah like it.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 16970 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u063a\u064f\u0636\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u062b\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31773,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/malik-sunnah-is-ark-of-nuh\/","url_meta":{"origin":33238,"position":3},"title":"Malik on Salvation: The Sunnah is like the Ark of Noah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Asakir reported: Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe Sunnah is like the Ark of Noah. Whoever boards it will be saved, and whoever does not board it wi